                            Due Diligence Checklist for Auto Shop Purchases
                        </h1>
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-6 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
                            <div class="flex items-center">
                                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=32&h=32&q=80" alt="Robert Kim" class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full mr-2">
